'From Squeak3.3alpha of 12 January 2002 [latest update: #4791] on 6 March 2002 at 12:18:54 am'!"Change Set:		rowCol-swDate:			5 March 2002Author:			Scott WallaceSupplies the missing functionality for the organize-into-row and organize-into-column commands available in the halo menu of a SelectionMorph"!!SelectionMorph methodsFor: 'halo commands' stamp: 'sw 3/6/2002 00:04'!organizeIntoColumn	"Place my objects in a column-enforcing container"	((AlignmentMorph inAColumn: selectedItems) setNameTo: 'Column'; color: Color orange muchLighter; enableDragNDrop: true; yourself) openInHand! !!SelectionMorph methodsFor: 'halo commands' stamp: 'sw 3/6/2002 00:04'!organizeIntoRow	"Place my objects in a row-enforcing container"	((AlignmentMorph inARow: selectedItems) setNameTo: 'Row'; color: Color orange muchLighter; enableDragNDrop: true; yourself) openInHand! !